Blackfang smiled. He took her and gently put her in a CR chamber, then
closed it.

He then opened a channel with the Predacon awaiting outside.

Blackfang: I know you can hear me, Pred. She's alright, past a
critical point, and I've just put her in CR. You'll have her back soon
enough.

--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, "raccoon7679" <raccoon7679@y...> wrote:
> KitKat::
> 
> She was starting to wake up. She could feel the gentle hand of a bot 
> stroking her head.  It took a bit of effort, but she managed a weak 
> smile. She sighed softly, feeling no more pain and feeling much 
> better, exhausted, but better. She slowly opened her optics and 
> looked up at Blackfang. She whispered, "thank you." and closed her 
> optics again.
> 
> 
> --- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, "Nic" <Proudwing500k@h...> wrote:
> > Blackfang leaned his back against a wall and started to chuckle. He
> > was exhausted from the stress, but at least this beauty was safe 
> now.
> > He decided she would recover better in CR.
> > 
> > He came closer to her and stroked her head.
> > 
> > Blackfang: Can you hear me? Are you still conscious?
> >
